%20Systematic%20Strategies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20quant%20arm%20of%20Point72%2C%20in%20September.%20He%20previously%20spent%20nearly%20two%20decades%20at%20systematic%20giant%20WorldQuant%2C%20including%20a%20long%20stretch%20as%20CIO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20interviewing%20quants%2C%20he's%20looking%20to%20suss%20out%20what%20kind%20of%20value%20a%20candidate%20added%20in%20their%20previous%20role%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he's%20also%20paying%20attention%20to%20how%20well%20they%20communicate%20this%20and%20whether%20their%20answers%20indicate%20authentic%20passion%20for%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSubstance%20matters%2C%20but%20what%20I'm%20really%20impressed%20by%20are%20candidates%20who%20have%20a%20structured%20thought%20process%2C%20can%20clearly%20articulate%20why%20they%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20previous%20mandates%2C%20and%20can%20bring%20passion%20to%20their%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Lauprete%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuant%20investing%20combines%20several%20specialties%20%E2%80%94%20quantitative%20analysis%2C%20programming%20and%20deploying%20code%2C%20and%20market%20knowledge%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20%26quot%3Bsomeone%20can%20articulate%20why%20putting%20these%20three%20things%20together%20is%20exciting%2C%20it's%20usually%20a%20reflection%20of%20their%20passion%2C%26quot%3B%20Lauprete%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrict%2C%20lengthy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-quant-battle-to-lock-up-traders-with-noncompetes-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enoncompetes%20are%20ubiquitous%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20systematic%20trading%2C%20with%20firms%20sometimes%20having%20to%20wait%20two%20years%20before%20a%20hire%20can%20join.%20Lauprete%20wants%20to%20%26quot%3Bunderstand%20how%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20structure%20their%20time%20off%20and%20what%20skills%20they'll%20be%20working%20on%20during%20that%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275df6755-850e-4a91-988a-6e3ab3b216d9%5C%22%3EJohn%20Cogman%2C%20CIO%20of%20Tower%20Research%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hypercompetitive%20quant%20job%20market%2C%20soft%20skills%20can%20set%20you%20apart%20and%20maximize%20your%20earning%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETower%20Research%20is%20one%20of%20the%20giants%20of%20quant%20proprietary%20trading%2C%20with%20over%201%2C100%20employees%20across%20a%20dozen%20global%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIdentifying%20and%20hiring%20top%20quants%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20important%20aspects%20of%20our%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20CIO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftower-research.com%2Fthe-myth-of-the-quant-god-why-humility-beats-genius%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJohn%20Cogman%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20paper%20titled%20%26quot%3BThe%20Myth%20of%20the%20Quant%20God.%26quot%3B%20Cogman%20said%20the%20challenge%20isn't%20just%20in%20finding%20technically%20gifted%20people%2C%20but%20those%20who%20also%20have%20the%20right%20demeanor%20and%20social%20IQ%20%E2%80%94%20a%20combo%20that%20%26quot%3Bis%20infinitely%20harder%20and%20far%20more%20valuable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuants%20who%20reach%20their%20full%20potential%20tend%20to%20share%20subtler%20traits%2C%26quot%3B%20Cogman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuantitative%20brilliance%20can%20be%20undercut%20by%20an%20inability%20to%20communicate%20ideas%20to%20other%20departments%2C%20like%20risk%20or%20engineering%2C%20by%20alienating%20coworkers%2C%20or%20by%20crumbling%20under%20market%20pressure%2C%20Cogman%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%2C%20not%20even%20the%20quant%20gods%20in%20our%20midst%2C%20is%20great%20at%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Cogman%20said.%20Those%20who%20plateau%20tend%20to%20lack%20self-awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20package%20for%20a%20quant%2C%20in%20Cogman's%20view%2C%20includes%20a%20mix%20of%20technical%20skills%20%E2%80%94%20modeling%2C%20programming%2C%20data%20analysis%2C%20and%20market%20know-how%20%E2%80%94%20combined%20with%20%26quot%3Btranslational%20skills%26quot%3B%20(communication%2C%20understanding%20the%20big-picture%20business%2C%20and%20adaptability)%20and%20%26quot%3Bbehavioral%20skills%26quot%3B%20like%20self-awareness%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20consistency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20that%20quantitative%20trading%20is%20a%20highly%20collaborative%20endeavor%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Blone-wolf%20geniuses%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20or%20overbearing%20jerks%20%E2%80%94%20aren't%20good%20for%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20most%20successful%20traders%20aren't%20necessarily%20the%20loudest%2C%20the%20flashiest%2C%20or%20the%20most%20strong-willed.%20They're%20the%20ones%20willing%20to%20learn%2C%20collaborate%2C%20and%20be%20self-critical%2C%26quot%3B%20Cogman%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20optimize%20empathy%20or%20quantify%20resilience%2C%20but%20they%20move%20the%20needle%20more%20than%20any%20parameter%20ever%20could.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225929c742-e9a3-49cd-b476-0523c7149415%5C%22%3EMike%20Tiano%2C%20deputy%20head%20of%20systematic%20strategies%20at%20Schonfeld%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20technical%20chops%2C%20from%20linear%20algebra%20to%20statistics%20to%20coding%2C%20are%20a%20given%2C%20a%20key%20trait%20Tiano%20%E2%80%94%20who%20was%20promoted%20to%20deputy%20head%20of%20systematic%20strategies%20in%20the%20fall%20%E2%80%94%20looks%20for%20is%20curiosity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20important%20trait%20is%20just%20obsessive%20curiosity%20about%20problems%2C%20especially%20outside%20of%20finance.%20Because%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20cross-fertilization%20that%20goes%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Tiano%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20it's%20physics%2C%20fluid%20mechanics%2C%20or%20biological%20evolution%2C%20many%20disciplines%20offer%20problem-solving%20frameworks%20that%20can%20be%20applied%20to%20systematic%20trading%2C%20including%20generating%20alpha%20signals%2C%20portfolio%20construction%2C