're%20doing%20because%20the%20markets%20are%20fair%20%E2%80%94%20you'll%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20on%20it.%20If%20you're%20deciding%20who%20to%20marry%20or%20who%20to%20have%20a%20relationship%20or%20whatever%2C%20you%20basically%20just%20plop%20into%20it%20without%20much%20thought.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20one%20has%20a%20gigantic%20impact%20on%20your%20life%20and%20one%20has%20a%20very%20small%20impact%20on%20your%20life.%20Yet%20we%20spend%20much%20more%20time%20worrying%20about%20the%20minor%20things%20and%20not%20enough%20time%20worrying%20about%20the%20big%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20notable%20year%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FBillAckman%2Fstatus%2F1989793183698714946%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinanciers%20offering%20dating%20advice%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Yass'%20romantic%20wisdom%20is%20pragmatic%2C%20though%20his%20solution%20may%20be%20more%20difficult%20to%20implement%20in%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20go%20out%20with%20somebody%20that%20your%20friends%20think%20is%20a%20nutcase%2C%26quot%3B%20Yass%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recommends%20asking%20your%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20and%20have%20them%20respond%20honestly%20and%20anonymously%20if%20possible%20%E2%80%94%20a%20single%20question%3A%20Am%20I%20making%20a%20gigantic%20mistake%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20many%20lives%20are%20ruined%20because%20you%20get%20involved%20with%20the%20wrong%20person%2C%20and%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20speak%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Yass%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285ebd16d-4ed8-43d9-9549-dec522a1bfe0%5C%22%3EGappy%20Paleologo%2C%20global%20head%20of%20quantitative%20research%20at%20Balyasny%20Asset%20Management%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPaleologo%20is%20known%20for%20offering%20memes%2C%20advice%2C%20and%20unvarnished%20views%20on%20LinkedIn%20and%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2F__paleologo%2Fstatus%2F1952563054866211141%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextended%20X%20thread%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20past%20summer%2C%20Paleologo%20offered%20advice%20to%20all%20the%20disappointed%20interns%20%E2%80%94%20people%20at%20top%20firms%20accustomed%20to%20succeeding%20at%20whatever%20they%20put%20their%20mind%20to%20%E2%80%94%20who%20fail%20to%20receive%20a%20full-time%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETime%20for%20a%20sober%2C%20but%20hopefully%20hopeful%2C%20possibly%20short%2C%20%F0%9F%A7%B5.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EEvery%20year%2C%20at%20this%20time%20of%20the%20year%2C%20I%20am%20contacted%20by%20several%20interns%20across%20a%20swat%20of%20HF%2Fprop%20trading%20firms%20who%20were%20just%20told%2C%20sometimes%20informally%2C%20that%20they%20will%20not%20receive%20return%20offers.%3Cbr%3E1%2F%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Gappy%20(Giuseppe%20Paleologo)%20(%40__paleologo)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F__paleologo%2Fstatus%2F1952563054866211141%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%205%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20first%20piece%20of%20advice%20is%20not%20to%20bottle%20it%20up%20and%20wallow%20in%20failure%20in%20isolation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20everyone%20has%20experienced%20at%20some%20point%20what%20you%20are%20experiencing%20now%2C%20and%20just%20the%20memory%20of%20rejection%20burns%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20if%20you're%20still%20set%20on%20a%20career%20in%20finance%2C%20start%20getting%20accustomed%20to%20the%20feeling%20of%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFinance%20is%20built%20out%20of%20being%20right%20only%20slightly%20more%20than%20being%20wrong.%20You%20don't%20learn%20how%20to%20succeed.%20You%20just