0Rolex%20is%20expected%20to%20remain%20king%2C%20Cartier%20is%20predicted%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20be%20in%20high%20demand%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-cartier-watch-engagement-photos-post-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPop%20icon%20Taylor%20Swift%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20gave%20the%20watches%20her%20stamp%20of%20approval.%20The%20singer%20was%20spotted%20wearing%20a%20Cartier%20Santos%20Demoiselle%20in%20her%20engagement%20announcement%20photos%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCartier%20has%20officially%20crossed%20from%20'fashion%20favorite'%20to%20'smart%20buy.'%26quot%3B%20Tutunikov%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20what%20style-driven%20clients%20want%2C%20but%20also%20what%20savvy%20buyers%20trust%20to%20hold%20value.%20In%202026%2C%20Cartier%20isn't%20slowing%20down%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20setting%20the%20pace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20models%20have%20driven%20the%20recent%20interest%20from%20Gen%20Z%20in%20particular%3A%20the%20entry-level%20Tank%2C%20the%20sportier%20Santos%2C%20and%20the%20dressy%20Panth%C3%A8re%2C%20Chrono24%20previously%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a3c8b46-1033-43ce-ae76-5a60786089fd%5C%22%3EDial%20size%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESmaller%20watches%2C%20suitable%20for%20everyday%20wear%2C%20are%20becoming%20more%20popular.%20Larger%20pieces%2C%20typically%20considered%20those%20more%20than%2040%20millimeters%2C%20are%20out%2C%20Altieri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCase%20sizes%20around%2036%20to%2040%20millimeters%2C%20clean%20dials%2C%20and%20versatile%20designs%20that%20work%20every%20day%20are%20resonating%20more%20than%20bold%20statement%20pieces%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReginald%20Ferguson%2C%20stylist%20and%20founder%20of%20New%20York%20Fashion%20Geek%2C%20said%2036%20to%2040%20millimeters%20will%20likely%20be%20the%20sweet%20s