's%20first%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJay%20Ong%2C%20the%20author%20of%20Jay's%20Brick%20Blog%2C%20a%20Lego%20news%20hub%20recognized%20by%20the%20company's%20ambassador%20network%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20this%20collection%20hits%20the%20sweet%20spot%20for%20adults%20who%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bvoracious%20appetite%20for%20toys%20and%20experiences%20that%20feed%20into%20their%20childhood%20nostalgia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20%26quot%3Bthe%20perfect%20marriage%20of%20two%20beloved%20brands%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20their%20respective%20popularities.%20Fans%20have%20been%20waiting%20decades%20for%20official%20Lego%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20sets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22399967f8-b149-4833-a7df-feb0f574cf8e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Perfect%20type%20of%20product%20for%20resellers'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%206%2C838-piece%20Venusaur%2C%20Charizard%2C%20and%20Blastoise%20set%20began%20appearing%20on%20eBay%20on%20Monday%20last%20week.%20The%20most%20expensive%20set%20that%20has%20sold%20since%20then%20cost%20%241%2C289.99.%20Others%20have%20resold%20for%20between%20%24690%20and%20%241%2C150%2C%20the%20listings%20show.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20item%20that%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20popular%20target%20for%20resellers%20was%20the%20free%20gift%20with%20purchase%2C%20or%20GWP%2C%20that%20came%20with%20the%20Venusaur%2C%20Charizard%2C%20and%20Blastoise%20set%3A%20the%20Kanto%20Region%20Badge%20Collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20badge%20collection%20consists%20of%20a%20312-piece%20video%20game%20collectible%20set%20described%20on%20the%20Lego%20website%20as%20%26quot%3Bnostalgic.%26quot%3B%20Scalpers%20are%20reselling%20this%20for%20north%20of%20%24200.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistorically%2C%20GWP%20sets%20have%20a%20very%20limited%20production%20run%2C%20so%20when%20they're%20sold%20out%2C%20Lego%20will%20usually%20not%20make%20any%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Tiago%20Catarino%2C%20a%20former%20Lego%20model%20designer%20and%2