0survey%20of%20US%20CEOs%20by%20the%20Yale%20School%20of%20Management%20shows%20that%20nearly%20two-thirds%20plan%20to%20maintain%20or%20reduce%20head%20count%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20average%20annual%20pay%20increases%20are%20forecast%20to%20remain%20flat%20in%202026%2C%20despite%20continued%20high%20inflation%20and%20after%20shrinking%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20according%20to%20Mercer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20factors%20may%20help%20explain%20why%20workers%20feel%20economically%20insecure.%20Nearly%20a%20third%20of%20Americans%20expect%20their%20finances%20to%20worsen%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20a%20December%20survey%20by%20Bankrate.%20That%20is%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20pessimism%20since%202018%2C%20when%20the%20personal-finance%20site%20began%20asking%20consumers%20about%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankrate.com%2Fdata-center%2Ffinancial-outlook%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20outlook%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgainst%20that%20backdrop%2C%20workers%20are%20increasingly%20reluctant%20to%20quit.%20The%20US%20quit%20rate%20has%20fallen%20below%20pre-pandemic%20norms%2C%20federal%20data%20show%2C%20even%20as%20more%20employers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-chief-adam-mosseri-announces-five-day-office-return-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emandate%20five%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20office%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-flags-employees-rto-office-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrack%20workers'%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fboss-track-ai-use-career-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20usage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20leaves%20workers%20with%20little%20appetite%20for%20pushback%2C%20said%20Jeff%20LeBlanc%2C%20a%20management%20lecturer%20at%20Bentley%20University.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20going%20to%20see%