.%20Her%20breakfast%20also%20packs%20in%20plenty%20of%20protein%20for%20muscle%20growth%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdietitian-shares-best-high-fiber-recipes-better-energy-gut-health-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efiber%20for%20gut%20health%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20up%20is%20coffee%20%E2%80%94%20Brink%20saves%20it%20for%20after%20the%20first%20meal%20of%20the%20day%2C%20to%20help%20provide%20more%20stable%20energy%20and%20prevent%20a%20crash%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20shifted%20to%20having%20my%20caffeine%20after%20I%20have%20my%20breakfast%2C%20which%20I%20feel%20like%20has%20made%20a%20huge%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrink%20also%20has%20a%20daily%20supplement%20regimen%20that%20includes%20iron%2C%20vitamin%20D%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreatine-most-effective-fitness-supplement-science-burn-fat-build-muscle-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emuscle-building%20creatine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20comes%20a%20chef-prepared%20lunch%20at%20the%20Sparks'%20training%20facility%2C%20where%20Brink%20often%20opts%20for%20two%20pieces%20of%20salmon%20with%20a%20side%20of%20Japanese%20sweet%20potatoes%20and%20asparagus.%20Lunch%20is%20followed%20by%20a%20nap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20day%2C%20Brink%20said%20she%20relies%20on%20snacks%20like%20bananas%2C%20dates%20with%20almond%20butter%2C%20or%20almonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20a%20game%2C%20her%20go-to%20fuel%20source%20is%20classic%20peanut%20butter%20and%20jelly%20sandwiches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20peanut%20butter%20and%20jelly.%20That's%20what%20really%20fuels%20me%20through%20the%20game%20is%20just%20having%20some%20of%20the%20protein%20from%20the%20peanut%20butter%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20carbs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20nights%20when%20she's%20not%20playing%2C%20Brink%20makes%20dinner%20with%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%2C%20fo