20says%20Meta's%20VR%20layoffs%20cut%20bloated%20in-house%20game%20studios%20that%20were%20quietly%20undermining%20the%20industry's%20ecosystem.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Fitzgerald%2FSportsfile%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOculus%20founder%20Palmer%20Luckey%20said%20Meta's%20VR%20layoffs%20don't%20signal%20retreat%20from%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20Meta's%20first-party%20VR%20studios%20were%20crowding%20out%20third-party%20developers%20across%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20cutting%20subsidized%20VR%20games%20lets%20Meta%20refocus%20on%20core%20tech%20and%20platform%20stability.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20decision%20to%20cut%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20jobs%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-closing-vr-horizon-workplace-app-reality-labs-layoffs-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReality%20Labs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20wind%20down%20parts%20of%20its%20metaverse%20strategy%20has%20reignited%20fears%20that%20the%20company%20is%20quietly%20backing%20away%20from%20virtual%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOculus%20founder%20Palmer%20Luckey%20says%20that%20interpretation%20is%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20and%20misses%20a%20deeper%20problem%20the%20cuts%20may%20actually%20solve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20X%20on%20Monday%2C%20Luckey%20said%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-layoffs-reality-labs-vr-horizon-worlds-teams-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta's%20Reality%20Labs%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%20were%20roughly%2010%25%20to%2015%25%20of%20the%20division's%2015%2C000%20employees%2C%20do%20not%20signal%20retreat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20still%20employs%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-cto-andrew-bosworth-reality-labs-all-hands-meeting-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elargest%20VR%20workforce%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20world%2C%20he%20said%2C%20dwarfing%20competitors%20%26quot%3Bby%20about%20an%20order%20of%20magnitude.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20numbers%20perspective%2C%20Luckey%20framed%20the%20layoffs%20as%20%26quot%3Bsix%20months%20of%20normal%20churn%20concentrated%20into%2060%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20not%20an%20existential%20blow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226113ed18-b0e7-438c-ac86-745eec395fac%5C%22%3EHow%20Meta's%20own%20VR%20studios%20distorted%20the%20industry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20consequential%20shift%2C%20he%20said%2C%20lies%20in%20where%20the%20cuts%20landed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Luckey%2C%20most%20of%20the%20eliminated%20roles%20were%20tied%20to%20first-party%20content%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-job-cuts-metaverse-reality-labs-ai-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta-owned%20studios%3C%2Fa%3E%20building%20internally%20developed%20VR%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20teams%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20become%20a%20growing%20problem%20for%20the%20broader%20VR%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeta%20heavily%20subsidizing%20their%20own%20(with%20money%2C%20marketing%2C%20placement%2C%20etc)%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20core%20technical%20progress%20and%20platform%20stability%20doesn't%20make%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20Luckey%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BCrowding%20out%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20entire%20ecosystem%2C%20even%20less%20so.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckey%20said%20third-party%20developers%20%E2%80%94%20even%20efficient%2C%20well-run%20studios%20%E2%80%94%20struggled%20to%20compete%20against%20Meta-owned%20teams%20backed%20by%20budgets%20that%20far%20exceeded%20what%20the%20market%20could%20realistically%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%2C%20he%20added%2C%20was%20that%20strong%20reviews%20and%20polished%20execution%20only%20worsened%20the%20imbalance%20by%20pulling%20attention%20and%20sales%20away%20from%20independent%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20point%20out%20that%20these%20teams%20did%20an%20awesome%20job%20and%20got%20awesome%20reviews%20from%20critics%20and%20customers%20alike%20%E2%80%94%20yes%2C%20and%20fucked%20up%20though%20it%20is%2C%20that%20makes%20the%20problem%20even%20worse!%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd6208f9-2e83-44ee-b007-7c5486523896%5C%22%3EA%20return%20to%20Oculus's%20ecosystem-first%20philosophy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20capital-constrained%20environment%2C%20Luckey%20said%2C%20Meta's%20resources%20are%20better%20spent%20on%20core%20technology%20and%20platform%20stability%20than%20on%20competing%20directly%20with%20developers%20it%20needs%20to%20keep%20VR%20viable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20framed%20the%20move%20as%20a%20return%20to%20Oculus's%20original%20philosophy.%20Internally%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20company%20aimed%20%26quot%3Bto%20NOT%20be%20Nintendo%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20avoiding%20a%20closed%2C%20first-party-dominated%20model%20in%20favor%20of%20building%20an%20ecosystem%20that%20others%20could%20profit%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckey%20acknowledged%20the%20human%20cost%20of%20layoffs%20and%20said%20he%20felt%20%26quot%3Breally%20bad%20for%20the%20people%20impacted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20said%20that%20scaling%20back%20first-party%20content%20is%20ultimately%20%26quot%3Ba%20good%20thing%20for%20the%20long-term%20health%20of%20the%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20if%20it's%20uncomfortable%20in%20the%20short%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalmer-luckey-meta-vr-layoffs-fix-deeper-industry-problem-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1768817663000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696dfab2a645d11881879479%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalmer-luckey-meta-vr-layoffs-fix-deeper-industry-problem-2026-1%22%2C