0into%20coding%2C%20debugging%2C%20and%20workflows.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20suggests%20candidates%20combine%20core%20engineering%20skills%20with%20AI%20expertise%20for%20career%20success.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Akaash%20Vishal%20Hazarika%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20senior%20software%20engineer%20based%20in%20Seattle.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-companies-employees-prove-productivity-rto-performance-reviews-ai-investments-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBig%20Tech%20employee%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20past%20eight%20years%2C%20working%20at%20Google%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Splunk%2C%20and%20now%20Salesforce.%20I've%20had%20a%20front-row%20seat%20to%20witness%20the%20changes%20in%20the%20tech%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20learned%20which%20skill%20sets%20software%20engineers%20need%20to%20land%20a%20job%20offer%20in%20the%20AI%20era.%20Tech%20companies%20agree%20that%20AI%20makes%20engineers%20more%20productive%2C%20so%20engineers%20are%20expected%20to%20use%20it%20to%20build%20things%20more%20quickly%20and%20reliably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20personally%20make%20heavy%20use%20of%20AI%20to%20help%20me%20with%20boilerplate%20stuff%20so%20that%20I%20can%20concentrate%20on%20the%20hard%20stuff%2C%20like%20system%20design%20and%20complex%20business%20logic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ee98df62-90f3-4ad8-930b-28f037ac0af4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPreparing%20to%20be%20a%20software%20engineer%20isn't%20the%20same%20as%20it%20was%20five%20years%20ago%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20interviewing%20for%20software%20engineering%20jobs%20in%202020%2C%20LeetCode%20and%20system%20design%20were%20the%20de%20facto%20standards%20for%20cracking%20a%20job%20interview.%20Job%20seekers%20who%20had%20an%20advanced%20understanding%20of%20data%20structures%20and%20algorithms%20would%20come%20out%20on%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20this%20is%20just%20the%20baseline%20expectation.%20AI%20is%20now%20widely%20used%20for%20coding%2C%20review%2C%20and%20design%2C%20so%20tech%20companies%2C%20especially%20startups%2C%20expect%20more%20from%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20skills%20remain%20the%20same%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenior-software-engineer-microsoft-ai-not-threat-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESoftware%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%20still%20need%20a%20problem-solving%20mindset%20and%20should%20know%20how%20to%20scale%20systems%20and%20leverage%20cloud%20services.%20New%20hires%20must%20now%20also%20understand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprompt-engineering-ai-chatgpt-jobs-explained-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprompt%20engineering%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20how%20to%20leverage%20AI%20to%20code%20a%20solution%20more%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20use%20AI%20for%20error%20handling%20and%20bug%20fixing.%20AI%20systems%20integration%20is%20another%20important%20new%20skill%20that%20involves%20incorporating%20AI%20into%20existing%20workflows%2C%20scaling%20AI%20systems%2C%20and%20determining%20when%20to%20use%20traditional%20versus%20AI%20solutions%20for%20business%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22368bc931-3674-4565-9131-84955c9c195e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInterviews%20have%20also%20evolved%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20still%20expected%20to%20have%20fundamental%20knowledge%20of%20core%20system%20design%2C%20data%20structures%2C%20and%20algorithms.%20You%20can%20still%20expect%20interviewers%20to%20test%20your%20problem-solving%20approaches%2C%20and%20if%20you%20know%20how%20to%20make%20the%20correct%20tradeoffs%20in%20time%20and%20space.%20Interviewers%20still%20care%20about%20debugging%20skills%2C%20since%20AI%20makes%20a%20lot%20of%20fundamental%20logic%20errors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20also%20need%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20some%20new%20things.%20I've%20seen%20firsthand%20that%20working%20with%20AI%20assistants%20in%20live%20screen-sharing%20mode%20is%20now%20allowed%20in%20some%20interviews.%20Interviewers%20are%20looking%20to%20see%20if%20you%20can%20help%20them%20achieve%20their%20business%20outcomes%20by%20combining%20software%20engineering%20skills%20with%20AI%20prompting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20I%20had%20with%20a%20Silicon%20Valley%20startup%20in%202024%2C%20I%20expected%20the%20hiring%20team%20to%20give%20traditional%20coding%20challenges.%20I%20was%20taken%20aback%20when%20I%20was%20given%20a%20huge%20code%20file%20and%20asked%20to%20debug%20a%20buggy%20behavior%2C%20and%20the%20interviewers%20explicitly%20said%20I%20could%20use%20AI%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ignored%20the%20invitation%20to%20use%20AI%2C%20thinking%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20do%20it%20myself%2C%20and%20ended%20up%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20on%20the%20problem%20to%20no%20avail.%20I%20failed%20that%20interview.%20That%20was%20an%20eye-opener%20for%20me%20about%20AI's%20new%20role%20in%20this%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20also%20be%20asked%20system%20design%20questions%20about%20where%20AI%20should%20be%20integrated%20into%20the%20current%20business%20workflow%2C%20or%20to%20discuss%20the%20trade-offs%20of%20using%20AI%20and%20traditional%20approaches%20in%20various%20problem%20contexts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20own%20system%20design%20interviews%2C%20I%20noticed%20companies%20starting%20to%20ask%20questions%20about%20how%20to%20integrate%20AI%20to%20enhance%20existing%20systems%20and%20support%20a%20particular%20model%20lifecycle%20in%20terms%20of%20infrastructure.%20What%20I've%20seen%20is%20that%20companies%20give%20access%20to%20a%20small%20codebase%20and%20expect%20you%20to%20deliver%20a%20small%20feature%20in%20about%20one%20hour%2C%20which%20is%20impossible%20without%20AI.%20With%20AI%2C%20you%20can%20roll%20it%20out%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20been%20asked%20behavioral%20questions%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20plan%20to%20evaluate%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20order%20to%20make%20the%20workflow%20better%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20plan%20to%20balance%20automation%20and%20manual%20oversight%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20new%20graduates%2C%20here's%20how%20to%20show%20hiring%20teams%20that%20you're%20equipped%20for%20the%20emerging%20needs%20of%20the%20software%20engineering%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c523b728-9083-4065-ae3f-52629254ac73%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Cultivate%20a%20production%20mindset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStart%20by%20contributing%20to%20open-source%20projects%20on%20AI%20or%20any%20other%20GitHub%20project.%20This%20demonstrates%20that%20you%20can%20navigate%20a%20production%20codebase%20and%20work%20on%20it%20independently%20to%20build%20a%20new%20feature%20or%20fix%20a%20bug.%20For%20solo%20repositories%2C%20include%20a%20README%20that%20explains%20the%20rationale%20for%20your%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a6ed970-7b41-4606-af25-e029f88e86df%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Build%20a%20portfolio%20of%20AI-integrated%20projects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIncorporate%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20traditional%20repositories%20to%20demonstrate%20hands-on%20experience%20with%20AI%20integration.%20Don't%20just%20deploy%20and%20run%20it%20locally%20%E2%80%94%20try%20to%20deploy%20it%20to%20the%20cloud.%20Many%20cloud%20providers%20provide%20free%20student%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22951bd26e-3ad4-42c3-9a9d-2c13a16d753f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Master%20cloud%20tooling%20and%20AI%20prompting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFocus%20on%20prompting%20AI%20to%20drive%20intended%20outcomes%20more%20effectively%20by%20providing%20structured%20input%20and%20output.%20Skills%20like%20AWS%20or%20GCP%20cloud%20certifications%20demonstrate%20your%20ability%20to%20be%20a%20keen%20learner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f905335b-f15e-4ab1-a6ab-db2f54e71f61%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Practice%20Leetcode-styled%20questions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELearn%20different%20problem-solving%20patterns%20and%20practice%20these%20skills%20regularly.%20Muscle%20memory%20and%20pattern%20recognition%20go%20a%20long%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20experienced%20software%20engineers%2C%20your%20biggest%20asset%20is%20your%20deep%20engineering%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20here%20are%20three%20tips%20that%20will%20help%20you%20in%202026%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22256aa0d6-254b-4ee2-9967-54d3d2044163%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Map%20your%20specialty%20with%20complementary%20AI%20skills%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPairing%20years%20of%20engineering%20expertise%20with%20impressive%20AI%20skills%20will%20get%20the%20attention%20of%20hiring%20managers.%20Consider%20boning%20up%20on%20these%20complementary%20skills%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBackend%3A%20Focus%20more%20on%20tasks%20related%20to%20scaling%20systems%2C%20especially%20AI%2C%20such%20as%20managing%20throughput%20and%20latency%20during%20deployment%20and%20maintaining%20versioning.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EData%20engineering%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBuild%20knowledge%20and%20skills%20in%20Kubeflow%2C%20MLFlow%2C%20Apache%20Spark%2C%20and%20Kinesis%20%E2%80%94%20these%20skills%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20important.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESite%20reliability%20engineering%3A%20Learn%20about%20SRE%2C%20which%20involves%20tracking%20AI%20usage%20and%20cost%2C%20and%20building%20fallback%20mechanisms%20when%20models%20misbehave%20in%20production.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227af69bb0-88cc-4418-8b34-850856a7ee70%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Develop%20an%20AI%20product%20mindset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESenior%20software%20engineers%20don't%20just%20build%3B%20they%20also%20need%20to%20strategize%20and%20innovate.%20Try%20to%20understand%20the%20trade-offs%20of%20relying%20on%20a%20third-party%20API%20versus%20using%20an%20open-source%20one%20and%20fine-tuning%20it%20for%20your%20business%20purposes.%20Questions%20on%20cost%2C%20reliability%2C%20and%20maintainability%20should%20always%20be%20top%20of%20mind%20as%20you%20develop%20an%20AI%20product%20mindset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5d98cfb-e656-4028-afaf-a4b79cca1b4f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Make%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20your%20current%20workplace%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIdentify%20workflows%20that%20have%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20manual%20involvement%20in%20your%20current%20job%2C%20and%20use%20AI%20to%20see%20if%20you%20can%20improve%20them.%20You%20can%20leverage%20AI%20to%20help%20you%20brainstorm%20on%20how%20to%20make%20it%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20veteran%20and%20newbie%20engineers%20should%20stay%20curious%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efind%20out%20the%20cool%20technologies%20and%20AI%20agents%20available%20in%20today's%20market%2C%20but%20don't%20abandon%20fundamental%20engineering%20approaches.%20The%20hybrid%20understanding%20of%20these%20technologies%20is%20what%20makes%20you%20valuable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20were%20interviewing%2C%20I'd%20position%20myself%20as%20a%20'hybrid%20engineer.'%20Don't%20just%20be%20a%20pure%20coder%20or%20just%20a%20prompt%20engineer.%20Be%20the%20bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-integration-transforming-software-engineering-hiring-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1768817101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696a9607e1ba468a96aa3ea8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-integration-transforming-software-engineering-hiring-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Akaash%20Vishal%20Hazarika%2C%20a%20senior%20software%20engineer%2C%20explains%20