%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework-from-home%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20remained%20fairly%20stable%20in%20recent%20years.%20He%20referred%20to%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bwork-from-home%20dark%20matter%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20invisible%20material%20that%20makes%20up%20much%20of%20the%20universe.%20Like%20dark%20matter%2C%20remote%20work%20appears%20to%20be%20widespread%2C%20Bloom%20said%2C%20but%20may%20often%20be%20procured%20through%20special%20exceptions%20or%20flying%20under%20the%20radar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20keep%20hearing%20endless%20stories%20of%20companies%20pushing%20employees%20to%20return%2C%20but%20we%20just%20don't%20see%20much%20of%20this%20in%20the%20survey%2C%20swipe-card%20or%20cellphone%20tracking%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20companies%2C%20the%20apparent%20disconnect%20between%20rising%20return-to-office%20mandates%20and%20actual%20office%20attendance%20raises%20questions%20about%20whether%20employees%20and%20managers%20are%20complying%20with%20RTO%20policies.%20For%20workers%2C%20it%20suggests%20there%20may%20be%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-negotiate-flexible-remote-work-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopportunities%20to%20work%20from%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20they%20realize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EHave%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20hiring%2C%20layoffs%2C%20or%20work%20life%20in%20Big%20Tech%2C%20Corporate%20America%2C%20or%20on%20Wall%20Street%3F%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSechTVqVWQve8iqYssNriCXdtwwdgGRixNNZpmslSKBQqIJ8g%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFill%20out%20this%20form%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejzinkula%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20via%20Signal%20a